high_descs: Turn around and move to the table.
Pick up the head of lettuce.
Turn left and move towards the wall and then turn left and move to the refrigerator.

Open the refrigerator door, place the head of lettuce on the top shelf, close the refrigerator door, wait, open the refrigerator door, pick up the lettuce from the top shelf and then close the refrigerator door.
Turn left and move towards the kitchen counter then turn right and face the table.
Place the head of lettuce to the left of the salt shaker on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled head of lettuce on a table.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the white table.
Pick up the head of lettuce.
Turn left and walk over to the fridge.
Chill the lettuce on the top shelf of the fridge then retrieve it and close the fridge again.
Turn left and walk until there is a white table to your right then turn to face the white table where there is an orange wine glass.
Put the lettuce between the orange glass and the large tomato.
anns.task_desc: Put cold lettuce on a white table.

high_descs: Turn around and move across the room to the white table with the lettuce on it.
Pick up the lettuce from the table.
Bring the lettuce to the fridge.
Open up the fridge, put the lettuce in the fridge, close the fridge, wait 5 seconds, open the fridge, pick up the lettuce from the fridge, close the fridge.
Bring the lettuce over to the table with the orange cup.
Put the lettuce on the table behind the orange cup.
anns.task_desc: Place the lettuce on the other table.
